      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my pride and joy. This beauty has been my reliable companion for a while now, and honestly, it still puts a smile on my face every time I turn the key. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who appreciates a car with a bit of soul. It\u2019s got a few tiny stories to tell on the exterior, but that just means it\u2019s been enjoyed the way a car should be! I\u2019ve kept it well-maintained and ready for its next adventure. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 29950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
