      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted performance machine, engineered for those who appreciate true mechanical synergy. This platform features a high-revving power plant with a broadened torque curve, paired to a crisp short-throw gearbox that delivers tactile engagement at every gate. The chassis has been dialed in with upgraded bushings and precision-tuned suspension geometry to eliminate compliance during high-lateral-G cornering. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system refresh and a high-flow exhaust system that optimizes backpressure for peak volumetric efficiency. No leaks, no codes, and zero deferred maintenance\u2014this is a turn-key build that punches way above its weight class.",
      "price": 38500.0,
